{"type":"text","timestamp":1782355354064,"sessionID":"ses_10368f325ffe1ty4VC2S3ocudF","part":{"id":"prt_efca7fe9e001D1PFuM3zKTcED7","messageID":"msg_efca7d358001Tdc4lwN8bGqK2u","sessionID":"ses_10368f325ffe1ty4VC2S3ocudF","type":"text","text":"Changed files:\n- `D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\plan.md`: wrote the human-readable migration plan with confirmed source behavior, target architecture, six implementation phases, test strategy, resource plan, missing inputs, and deferred risks.\n- `D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\plan.json`: wrote a strict JSON plan with required top-level keys, concrete target file/module ownership, assets, dependency replacement strategy, test obligations, six canonical phases, implementation groups, analysis gaps, source overrides, and deferred items.\n\nCommands run:\n- `& 'C:\\Users\\Sieger\\AppData\\Local\\Programs\\Python\\Python312\\python.exe' '-m' 'json.tool' 'D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\plan.json' | Out-Null`\n\nBuild result:\n- NOT RUN. No HarmonyOS build gate was executed in this planning-only session; only the required plan artifact validation command was run.\n\nPlan changes:\n- Added a complete phased plan covering bootstrap/resources, startup/navigation/session, onboarding/login/profile, home/history discovery, detail/cart state mutations, and polish/tests/verification.\n- Bound implementation groups to concrete source paths, methods, target domains, required behaviors, and acceptance evidence instead of broad shell ownership.\n- Recorded source-backed architecture decisions:\n  - real persisted state is login-only\n  - most app content is static fixture data plus in-memory session state\n  - startup route selection is splash-gated\n  - search/filter controls are local UI state, not real repository filtering\n- Recorded source overrides against static-analysis noise:\n  - media library, SAF/file access, runtime permissions, and notification/widget capabilities are not currently source-backed behaviors\n- Captured resource scope:\n  - all 52 source strings\n  - colors/themes\n  - drawable/mipmap assets\n  - startup/app icon metadata\n- Captured test scope:\n  - source example tests are boilerplate only\n  - target-side tests should focus on startup/session, login validation, selection commands, detail state, and pure helpers\n- Missing inputs noted in plan:\n  - `translation-inputs/plan-validation-report.md`\n  - `translation-inputs/plan-validation-report.json`\n  - `translation-inputs/phase-task-checklist.md`\n  - `translation-inputs/phase-task-checklist.json`\n  - `translation-inputs/phase-capability-checklist.md`\n  - `translation-inputs/phase-capability-checklist.json`\n  - `translation-inputs/test-build-reports/`\n  - several Kotlin sidecar summaries like `compose-map.json`, `navigation-map.json`, `viewmodel-map.json`, `repository-map.json`, `flow-livedata-map.json`\n  - `translation-inputs/mapcir/skeleton-hybrid/`\n- Plan coverage:\n  - covers startup, navigation, onboarding, login, logout, home discovery, history favourites, restaurant selection, detail expansion/like/cart-visibility behavior, cart rendering, resources, and target-side verification strategy.\n\nDeferred issues:\n- `deferred-detail-cart-consistency`, owner `phase-05-detail-cart-state-mutations`: source detail quantity state is local while cart reads a separate snapshot; later implementation may need an explicit parity note if this remains simplified.\n- `deferred-runtime-capability-row-cleanup`, owner `phase-06-polish-tests-verification`: capability and matrix rows still need narrow post-planning cleanup to downgrade heuristic false positives with exact source evidence.\n- `deferred-test-harness-availability`, owner `phase-06-polish-tests-verification`: runnable `cjpm test` support depends on the target skeleton and may need follow-up harness repair.\n\nNext recommended action:\n- Run the separate narrow `planning-phase-backfill` session to apply row-level `plannedPhase` updates to `source-coverage-matrix.json/md` and `platform-capability-check.json/md` using this new phase/group plan as authority.","time":{"start":1782355328670,"end":1782355354063}}}
